THE GAME
--------

  'X_Next' is a Workbench game where you have to move to all the
tiles that are shown on the game board. You can move to any tile
except those that are immediately next, either horizontally,
vertically or diagonally, to your position. As you leave a tile,
it disappears, unless it has a number on it, in which case that
number will decrease by one. When you complete a board, X_Next
displays a new board and the game continues...

  Have fun!

